    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "peace? i don't even know what that means anymore. everything just feels heavy. like i'm just dragging this corpse of a career around. it's like no matter what i do, the world just keeps pushing back. it's just... constant. why does it have to be so hard to just exist?",
